title: ‘The Great British Baking Show’ Episode 7: “Custard Week” | Everything Is Cake
description:
Kate and Amelia recap the highs and lows of “Custard Week,” including a floating signature, a dramatic staggered technical, and a fabulous set custard showstopper, before handing out some awards.
Hosts: Kate Halliwell and Amelia Wedemeyer
Producer: Sasha Ashall
